                "100003_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "真是个难缠的家伙……\\n我可真佩服我自己。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界卢卡",
            "context": "我还有一战之力……\\n决不能在这里放弃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我能明白你们的心情……\\n不过，你们是没法战胜我们的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "可恶……\\n我们的力量明明是一样的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这并不是实力的问题。\\n我反而很好奇，\\n为什么你们不明白原因。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你们一定满脑子都是烦恼吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你们认为跟随尤蒂尔\\n并不是正确的选择，\\n却又不清楚分道扬镳是否正确。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "心怀迷茫的你们\\n是不可能战胜我们的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_13"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我们是不会败给\\n你们这些抛弃了信赖的家伙的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "啧，又是信赖。\\n你们真的是除了这句\\n就没有别的话可说了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "就让你们亲眼见证一下\\n那所谓的信赖是\\n多么经不起考验的东西吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_13"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伙伴们",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "不会吧！又来了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这应该又是来自于\\n另一个世界的我们吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "如果只是来自于异界的我们的话，\\n也许未必是敌人，不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_13"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！\\n可恶……果然是这样吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "现在明白了吧？\\n无数可能性当中，你们所谓的信赖\\n能坚持到最后的反而是少数。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n多谢你告诉我们这个好消息。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你说什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我想你应该是想通过告诉我们\\n信赖有多脆弱来破坏我们的信赖。\\n但你这纯属徒劳。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "如果我们的信赖是一种奇迹，\\n那这对我们来说\\n更是一件值得骄傲的事情！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "是吗……\\n你们的想法似乎还挺坚定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "只不过，无数可能性的世界当中，\\n大多数的你们却憎恨着尤蒂尔。\\n这便是事实。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唔！出现了不止一个！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "他们都是对尤蒂尔\\n心怀怨恨的我们吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "好了，和你们自己尽情厮杀吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "让我好好欣赏一下，\\n究竟是将信赖视如珍宝的你们能活下来，\\n还是抛弃了信赖的你们能复仇成功吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔！等等，贝维特哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "啊！亲爱的，小心！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "穆穆！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我、我没事……\\n先别管我，你看那边……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是耶梦加得他们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "是异界的我们……\\n看到他们守卫要塞的时候\\n我就猜到了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "我可先说明白了，\\n我没有在操控这些龙哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "只不过对尤蒂尔\\n心怀怨恨的不仅是人类而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界碧龙",
            "context": "……\\n这不是怨恨，是世界之理。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "世界之理……也许是吧。\\n就算异界的我与异界的尤蒂尔为敌，\\n也并不值得惊讶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "因为人与龙原本就无法共存。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界碧龙",
            "context": "没错。异界的我啊，\\n不要再服从于人类了，\\n那只会孕育悲伤和绝望。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我说耶梦加得！\\n你怎么还和那胡言乱语的家伙\\n产生共鸣了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "不是胡言乱语。\\n人与龙无法共存……\\n这件事你应该比谁都明白不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "你到底想说什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "我想说的当然就和你想的一样。\\n你和尤蒂尔终成眷属的\\n幸福未来根本就不会到来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "你一直都是这么认为的不是吗？\\n你很清楚人与龙是\\n不可能走到一起的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "所以又怎样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "不要小瞧我。\\n你以为这点小事就能改变\\n我对亲爱的的心意吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "不……你应该很清楚，\\n尤蒂尔的眼里\\n根本就没有你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "你也早就明白了吧？\\n你永远无法成为尤蒂尔\\n心中最特别的那个人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "亲爱的最为珍视的并不是我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "不知道你还能\\n骗自己到什么时候。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "你想说的就只有这些？\\n到头来不过是你没能坚持对他的爱吧？\\n不要把我和你相提并论。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界绯龙",
            "context": "我当然坚持过。\\n我不曾放弃对他的爱，\\n直到……亲爱的亲手杀了我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "什么！？亲爱的……杀了你！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界碧龙",
            "context": "大多数世界之中\\n五龙都有着相同的结局。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界碧龙",
            "context": "五龙……\\n几乎都是由尤蒂尔亲手杀死。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我竟然……\\n亲手杀了……五龙吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "才、才不是呢！\\n你说的那是魔神搞的鬼吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界碧龙",
            "context": "当然，其中也有被魔神附身的\\n尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界碧龙",
            "context": "但即便是在消灭了魔神的世界里，\\n人与龙的对立也不可避免地发生，\\n五龙也最终都死在尤蒂尔手中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "怎、怎么会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "异界碧龙",
            "context": "世界之理无法改变。\\n人与龙本就不应尝试共存。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "你刚才说，\\n服从人类只会孕育悲剧和绝望对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_03_0067",
